  "questionProse": [
    "¿Por qué se usa el elemento `<source>`?"
  ],
  "questionCode": [],
  "explanationProse": [
    "El [`<source>` element is used to specify available media formats](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-us/docs/web/html/element/source).\n\n    Se usa específicamente con los elementos [`<video>`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video), [`<audio>`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/audio) y [`<picture>`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/picture), permitiendo que el navegador elija el formato más adecuado."
  ],
